WEBVTT

1
00:18:49.200 --> 00:18:53.740 
爱德华和爱琳娜互相喜欢
I believe that Edward and Elinor have formed an attachment.

2
00:18:53.910 --> 00:18:58.420 
我不忍叫她这么快走 迪凡郡太远了
It would be cruel to take her away so soon. Devonshire is so far.

3
00:18:59.210 --> 00:19:02.420 
为啥这么严肃 你觉得他不适合她
Why so grave? Do you disapprove her choice?

4
00:19:02.590 --> 00:19:04.760 
没有啊
By no means.

5
00:19:04.920 --> 00:19:09.760 
-爱德华很和善 -和善 可是呢
-Edward is very amiable. -Amiable? But?

6
00:19:09.930 --> 00:19:12.350 
可是总缺少了什么
There is something wanting.

7
00:19:12.510 --> 00:19:15.520 
他太严肃了 他昨晚读诗的样子
He is too sedate. His reading last night...

8
00:19:15.680 --> 00:19:19.100 
爱琳娜不像你 他的克制适合她
Elinor has not your feelings. His reserve suits her.

9
00:19:19.270 --> 00:19:21.020 
他真的爱她吗
Can he love her?

10
00:19:21.190 --> 00:19:25.610 
如此相敬如宾就能满足吗
Can the soul really be satisfied with polite affections?

